    "body": "Thanks for the explanation @bengotow. Makes sense.\n\nI'm surprised there is no easy way to have a notification triggered by a window show the window. Right now I have to do this and proxy the notification event through to the main process and handle it there: https://github.com/sindresorhus/caprine/blob/8106f5060b259833111a6b7c69ed761a39f7408a/browser.js#L23-L36\n\n@zcbenz Would you be open to adding a `notification-click` event to the browser window webContents?\n"
